{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762169288852","path":null,"data":{"id":814,"title":"AIA: 推出「全程守護健康保」","type":"PRODUCT_NEWS","time":1641264862218,"tags":["友邦保險"],"content":"<p style=\"line-height: 2; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">致合作夥伴：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>「全程守護健康保<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">」</span></strong><strong>(HJG)</strong></span> 將於<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>2022年1月11日</strong></span>（首個申請日期）正式推出，產品特點如下：</span></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\"><strong>每年高達30</strong><strong>次門診服務</strong></span>（香港醫療網絡）</span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\"><strong>市場首創</strong></span>：家中康復治療及家中善終關懷服務</span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">每3年享一次免費醫療檢查服務</span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\"><strong>人生階段保障</strong></span>：於人生不同階段提供健康評估及疫苗提供實報實銷癌症保障</span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\"><strong>個人療程管理服務與復康管理</strong></span>：適用於此產品所有計劃</span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color: #e67e23; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>保證終身續保</strong></span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\"><strong> 保費相宜</strong></span>：以20歲非吸煙男性以年繳方式投保AIA健康系列：「全程守護健康保」附加契約版本為例，首年保費平均每日約 HK$９</span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\"><strong>新增</strong></span>：附加契約版本可附加指定醫療基本計劃如AIA自願醫保靈活計劃及特級「健康之寶」2等</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 詳情請參閱附件。</span></p>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"> <!--EndFragment--></span></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"><!--EndFragment--></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!--EndFragment--></span></p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"Ref A2021338.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2022-01-04/d76bfc72ce964eeca1fad61bbe22f65f.pdf","uploadTime":1641268307844,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"全程守護健康保.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2022-01-04/de997e51167c44fbba9e080770653d9f.pdf","uploadTime":1641268315423,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"Health Journey Guardian.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2022-01-04/3461c979a03943ca9184ce266d5b9f30.pdf","uploadTime":1641268315431,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"基本計劃年繳保費表.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/C